com.dotmarketing.plugin.business

Interface PluginAPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PluginAPIImpl

    public interface PluginAPI
    Since:
    1.6.5c The PluginAPI is intended to provide access/information on the different plugins. It can also provide the plugins the ability to retrieve their property values. The methods starting with load are expected to goto cache first and then database and methods starting with find will typically hit database always.
    Author:
    Jason Tesser, Andres Olarte
